title: Add G-UNI (ERC20 UniswapV3 Positions) as collateral to Aave’s AMM market
body:
G-UNI is an ERC20 wrapper on any Uniswap V3 position with a specified price range (in the case of the stablecoin pairs relevant here, the ranges are fixed and immutable). 

Pairs to be onboarded as collateral:
G-UNI DAI/USDC 
G-UNI USDC/USDT
G-UNI DAI/USDT

These fungible tokens allow Uniswap V3 liquidity to function as collateral in lending and borrowing markets like Aave. Read full proposal here: https://governance.aave.com/t/arc-add-gelato-s-g-uni-erc20-uniswap-v3-positions-as-collateral-to-aave-s-amm-market/5687
author: 0x88215a2794ddC031439C72922EC8983bDE831c78
